description:
Cameron is about 5'5" and is a powder keg of energy.
He is from the mid-west, and his group of friends are mostly African Americans- a notable fact because he definitely has got the home boy rapper style.
Black hair, long lashes, and crystal blue eyes are only the first of many his remarkable traits. That back door of his is rock hard, and thankfully he is not shy about showing it off.
I'm hoping to work more with him in the future, so cross your finger that he will be back!
Enjoy!
title: Cameron - Solo
